<br>
1st... what is your skill lvl?<br>
<br>
2nd... explain how i can make 8 / 11 bracers<br>
         and then how i can make 1 / 25 pauldrons?<br>
<br>
please note.... i have made many 1 sheet items with a high success rate, however i have attempted MANY 2 sheet combines, and as such have had a much larger failure rate..<br>
<br>
I refer to trivials on Fine Steel... 1 sheet combines trivials are lower than 2 sheet and 3 sheet. <br>
Darkscale armour trivials at &gt;250... which means above 250. This does not mean that each piece is a trivial of 250.<br>
<br>
Some may trivial at 252, other pieces may trivial at 260 for all we know. VI have not given us the option to see beyond 250, the only information they have allowd us is.... &gt;250 &lt;-- must be hard then. <br>
<br>
refer again to mistletoe sickles.... <br>
In 20 attempts, i create up to 5 sickles...<br>
compare that to crimson darkscale bracers/visors/gorgets and boots<br>
In 20 attempts, i create up to 16 items.<br>
<br>
Every trade skiller has their own opinions, however i have proven my opinions to myself, and am firm in those beliefs..<br>
<br>
